<BaseLayout pageTitle="Michael Dijkstra's Work - Product Designer and Full Stack Developer" pageDescription="Michael Dijkstra's Work. Product Designer and Full Stack Developer based in Sydney, Australia." logo="true" bodyClass="bg-eerie text-white font-sans">
